snippet.title: Freedom Fighters - Story Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for Freedom Fighters for Playstation 2, Xbox, Gamecube and PC
This game was developed by I/O Interactive and published by Electronic Arts.
Freedom Fighters had fantastic and ahead of its time multiplayer
